  overflow: hidden;
}

  -webkit-align-items: center;
  background-color: #DDD;

  visibility: visible;
}

  #sub-frame-error-details {
    display: none;
  }

  overflow: hidden;
}

  -webkit-align-items: center;
  background-color: #DDD;

  visibility: visible;
}

  #sub-frame-error-details {
    display: none;
  }
